The forty-ninth letter of the Khanty alphabet
The first letter of the Khanty alphabet, written in the Cyrillic script.

(Kazym) very
Пәмащипа, шєӈк єпԓӑӈ вәс. ― Pəmaŝipa, šêňk êpḷăň wəs. ― Thank you, it was very delicious.
